@node c11 "Chapter 1.1"
Date: 15-10-98   Version: 0.11

This guide is far from complete. I just tried to make it available in this 
version and tried to make all information in these online help-files as
true and updated as possible.

The 303tracker online help contains a number of individual help-files;
these files are all in AmigaGuide format so you can also read them with
Multiview.

Jeroen Schellekens.
@endnode

@node c15 "Chapter 1.5"
This picture shows you the  @{"Diagram" link /images/BlockDiagram.ilbm/main}
block diagram of 303tracker
which gives a good overview
of the total functionality
of 303tracker.

There are 3 @{b}generators@{ub} in
303tracker:

1. TB-303 Bassline
2. Drum Machine
3. Synchronising Sample

Then these 3 channels
route into a @{b}mixer@{ub} with
individual @{b}volumes@{ub} and
@{b}equalizers@{ub} (Low Band &
High Band)

Then the mix is put into
a @{b}effects-list@{ub} which
contains several effects
and can be placed in any
order.


At this moment, only these modules are available:

- 303sequencer
- TB-303 Bassline engine.

In future, the rest will be added.

@endnode

@node How2or " "
@{"        How to order 303tracker?        " link /images/howkop.ilbm/main}   Date: 15-10-98   Version: 0.11


At this moment it's still not possible to order a version of 303tracker.
This due to the fact that 303tracker is not ready yet for a final, official
release 1.0.

When it's time to release version 1.0 of 303tracker, it will split into a
full commercial version and a demo version with a number of limitations and
features which are disabled.

The full version will be distributed by a number of publishers and
companies. The price of it is not determined yet, expect to pay around
$50 US dollars for it.

Until that time, a free 303tracker demo along with info are available at:

http://www.xs4all.nl/~jes303     Aminet: /mus/edit/303tracker.lha
       www.xs4all.nl/~mjk303
       www.dutch.nl/net

You can contact by emailing to: @{b}jes303@xs4all.nl@{ub}

Jeroen Schellekens, author of 303tracker.
@endnode
